"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-kids-2024-0722-1461221-paris-olympics-team-ireland\", \"text\": \"  The Olympic Games are up and running! Team Ireland have a record 133 athletes going for gold!! They have done the hard work to get there and now we need all the boys and girls in Ireland to cheer them on.  Check out the cool promo starringJack Woolleywho will be competing inTaekwondo (58kg).  RT\\u00c9jr are supporting the green machine. On ourInstaandTikTokwe meet the athletes and ask them the tough questions like what is their fave pizza topping?!  All across RT\\u00c9we are Ready for the Moment with our own top team! Fans can watch 14 hours a day of coverage across three daily TV programmes on RT\\u00c92 and RT\\u00c9 Player.  RT\\u00c9.ie have a cool website with all the latest news fromParis 2024. Meet ALL the Team Ireland starshere!  And we are all over socials too on X, Insta and TikTok with RT\\u00c9 Sport, RT\\u00c9 News and more!  RT\\u00c9 Radio 1 will have live coverage of the major action and updates across the regular shows as well as 2fm's Game On and much more.  For all the latest news check out Paris 2024 on RT\\u00c9.ie.          \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026. RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media. RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.  Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\"}"